♪ WHEN THE EDGE
OF SURRENDER'S IN SIGHT ♪

00:28.158 --> 00:30.769
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY

00:30.900 --> 00:33.816
♪ IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT

00:36.471 --> 00:38.864
♪ 'CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY

